The Glenn Beck Program

      The Glenn Beck Program - 3/18/14Tuesday, March 18, 2014 10:28 AM



See Glenn's reaction to the president's Sanctions against Russia
            and his faltering position on the entire Russian approach.

  Also, Glenn has discovered a new band from Iceland,

  Plus, wait until you hear NASA's new report
